# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment variables — copy to .env.local for local dev (never commit .env.local)
# On Vercel: add these in Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Required ─── session security (generate a random 32-char+ string)
SESSION_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-secret

# Required ─── base path (always "/" on Vercel root domain)
BASE_PATH=/

# Optional ─── override default admin username (default: "admin")
ADMIN_USERNAME=admin

# Optional ─── OpenRouter API key (enables AI article generation & keyword scoring)
# Get one at https://openrouter.ai/keys  (free tier available)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# Optional ─── Google AdSense publisher ID
# ADSENSE_PUBLISHER_ID=

# NOTE: On Vercel the JSON file database lives in /tmp and resets on cold starts.
# Articles, settings, and redirects saved through the admin panel persist within
# a single function instance lifetime.  For durable storage connect a Postgres
# database and swap lib/db.ts for a Drizzle/Prisma adapter.
